<section class="ks-testimonials">
  <div class="ks-testimonials-inner">
    <div class="ks-section-header">
      <span class="ks-section-eyebrow">Verified Reviews</span>
      <h2 class="ks-section-title">Worn By Believers</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="ks-testimonials-grid">
      <div class="ks-testimonial-card">
        <div class="ks-testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="ks-testimonial-quote">"The details are incredible. It's a great daily reminder of what Jesus did for me. I wear it everywhere — gym, pool, shower."</p>
        <div class="ks-testimonial-author">Dima G.</div>
        <div class="ks-testimonial-verified">✓ Verified Purchase</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ks-testimonial-card">
        <div class="ks-testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="ks-testimonial-quote">"Great quality and an even better message. I've bought multiples for myself and as gifts. Everyone asks where I got it."</p>
        <div class="ks-testimonial-author">Latrell J.</div>
        <div class="ks-testimonial-verified">✓ Verified Purchase</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ks-testimonial-card">
        <div class="ks-testimonial-stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="ks-testimonial-quote">"Had it over a year, wear it daily — gym, shower, pool. Still holding up great. The lifetime guarantee is real."</p>
        <div class="ks-testimonial-author">Rayyan M.</div>
        <div class="ks-testimonial-verified">✓ Verified Purchase</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.ks-testimonials {
  padding: 100px 40px;
  background: #1A1A1A;
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
}
.ks-testimonials::before {
  content: '"';
  position: absolute;
  top: -40px;
  left: 50%;
  transform: translateX(-50%);
  font-family: 'Cinzel', serif;
  font-size: 400px;
  color: rgba(201,168,76,0.03);
  line-height: 1;
  pointer-events: none;
}
.ks-testimonials-inner {
  max-width: 1200px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.ks-testimonials-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: 24px;
  margin-top: 60px;
}
.ks-testimonial-card {
  background: #0A0A0A;
  border: 1px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.12);
  padding: 36px;
  transition: border-color 0.3s;
}
.ks-testimonial-card:hover {
  border-color: rgba(201,168,76,0.35);
}
.ks-testimonial-stars {
  color: #C9A84C;
  font-size: 14px;
  margin-bottom: 20px;
  letter-spacing: 3px;
}
.ks-testimonial-quote {
  font-family: 'Cormorant Garamond', serif;
  font-size: 18px;
  font-style: italic;
  color: #F5F0E8;
  line-height: 1.7;
  margin-bottom: 24px;
}
.ks-testimonial-author {
  font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
  font-size: 11px;
  font-weight: 700;
  letter-spacing: 2px;
  color: #C9A84C;
  text-transform: uppercase;
}
.ks-testimonial-verified {
  font-family: 'Barlow Condensed', sans-serif;
  font-size: 10px;
  color: #888888;
  letter-spacing: 1px;
  margin-top: 4px;
}
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .ks-testimonials-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
  .ks-testimonials { padding: 60px 20px; }
}
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "KS Testimonials",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{ "name": "KS Testimonials" }]
}
{% endschema %}
